title: Post Stresemann Succession DVP Congress
subtitle: The weight of his death is truly big...
tags: event
view-if: (year = 1929 and month = 11 and stresemann_dead) or (dvp_congress_timer <= 0) and dvp_votes > 0
new-page: true
max-visits: 1
on-arrival: dvp_congress_timer = 48

= Post Stresemann congress

The atmosphere inside the convention hall is thick with cigar smoke, nervous whispers, and an overarching sense of dread. Gustav Stresemann is gone. The man who single-handedly held the Deutsche Volkspartei together—and frequently anchored the Weimar Republic itself—has left behind an ideological vacuum that threatens to rip the party apart.

On one side, the reformist left-wing demands a continuation of the Grand Coalition with the SPD. On the other, the heavy industrialists of the right-wing demand a sharp turn toward the DNVP. 

The ballots are cast, counted, and the final tally is announced from the podium...

- @winner_dvp_1929_congress: And the power gains...

@winner_dvp_1929_congress
on-arrival: {!

Q.dvp_curtius = Q.dvp_curtius || 0;
Q.dvp_luther = Q.dvp_luther || 0;
Q.dvp_scholz = Q.dvp_scholz || 0;

if (Q.dvp_reform_outcome == "stresemann_success") {
    Q.dvp_curtius += 3;
    Q.dvp_luther += 1;
    Q.dvp_scholz -= 1;
} else if (Q.dvp_reform_outcome == "scholz_victory") {
    Q.dvp_scholz += 4;   // Scholz has existing institutional momentum
    Q.dvp_curtius -= 2;
} else {
    Q.dvp_luther += 3;
    Q.dvp_curtius += 1;
    Q.dvp_scholz += 1;
}

Q.dvp_right *= 0.01;
Q.dvp_left *= 0.01;

Q.dvp_curtius += Q.dvp_left
Q.dvp_scholz += Q.dvp_right
Q.dvp_luther += (Q.dvp_left + Q.dvp_right) / 2;

var max_score = Math.max(Q.dvp_curtius, Q.dvp_luther, Q.dvp_scholz);

// ==========================================
// 5. FINAL OUTCOME ROUTER EVALUATION
// ==========================================
if (Q.dvp_curtius > (Q.dvp_luther + Q.dvp_scholz) / 2 && Q.dvp_curtius > Q.dvp_luther && Q.dvp_curtius > Q.dvp_scholz) {
    Q.dvp_successor_outcome = "curtius_victory";
    Q.dvp_party_leader = "Julius Curtius";
    Q.dvp_ideology = "National Liberalism";
} else if (Q.dvp_luther > (Q.dvp_curtius + Q.dvp_scholz) / 2 && Q.dvp_luther > Q.dvp_curtius && Q.dvp_luther > Q.dvp_scholz) {
    Q.dvp_successor_outcome = "luther_victory";
    Q.dvp_party_leader = "Hans Luther";
    Q.dvp_ideology = "National Liberalism";
} else if (Q.dvp_scholz > (Q.dvp_curtius + Q.dvp_luther) / 2 && Q.dvp_scholz > Q.dvp_curtius && Q.dvp_scholz > Q.dvp_luther) {
    Q.dvp_successor_outcome = "scholz_victory";
    Q.dvp_party_leader = "Ernst Scholz";
    Q.dvp_ideology = "National Liberalism (Scholzite)";
} else {
    Q.dvp_successor_outcome = "eduard_victory";
    Q.dvp_party_leader = "Eduard Dingeldey";
    Q.dvp_ideology = "National Liberalism (Dingeldist)";
}

!}
go-to: curtius_victory if dvp_successor_outcome = "curtius_victory"; luther_victory if dvp_successor_outcome = "luther_victory"; scholz_victory if dvp_successor_outcome = "scholz_victory"; eduard_victory if dvp_successor_outcome = "eduard_victory"

